guarded formula characterizing all counter-examples:
"∃ pke n #i.
  (Commit( pke, 'Issuer', n ) @ #i)
 ∧
  (∀ #j. (Issuer_Init( 'Issuer' ) @ #j) ⇒ ⊥) ∧
  (∀ RevealEvent Entity #kr.
    (KeyReveal( RevealEvent, Entity ) @ #kr) ∧ (Honest( Entity ) @ #i) ⇒ ⊥)"
*/
by sorry

